         <div xml:id="alalal-e35263"><!-- l3d9a10 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-e35263-Hd1e99">Articulus 10</head>
            <head xml:id="alalal-e35263-Hd1e101" type="question-title">Qua specie cultus Christus debeat coli?</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e35263-d1e104">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="20"/>ARTICULUS X.
<lb ed="Bd" n="21"/>Qua specie cultus Christus debeat coli?
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e35263-d1e111">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="22"/>Deinde quaeritur de hoc quod dicit,
<lb ed="Bd" n="23"/>ibi, B, circa medium: <quote xml:id="alalal-e35263-Qd1e117"> Si Filius non
<lb ed="Bd" n="24"/>est Deus natura, se√© creatura : nec 
colen<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="25"/>dus est, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e35263-d1e125">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="26"/>Contra: Non est ejusdem colere, ei
<lb ed="Bd" n="27"/>coli, Filius autem coluit Patrem, orando,
<lb ed="Bd" n="28"/>offerendo, objiciendo: ergo videtur, quod
<lb ed="Bd" n="29"/>coli latria non debeat.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e35263-d1e137">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="30"/>Ab woc dicendum, quod Christus 
de<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="31"/>bet coli latria: licet enim coluerit, hoc
<lb ed="Bd" n="32"/>fecilin quantum homo fuit, et mediator
<lb ed="Bd" n="33"/>Dei et hominum. Unde utrumque 
com<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="34"/>petit ei, et unum non excludit religuum :
<lb ed="Bd" n="35"/>sicut secundum hominem minor est 
Pa<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="36"/>tre, et secundum Deum aequalis.
</p>
         </div>
